<span id="freeTextContainer11894297084065078668">If you look for <s>fuckery</s> intrigue, especially tagged with such words as &quot;women&quot;, &quot;revenge&quot;, &quot;manipulation&quot; and &quot;wtf is going on here&quot; - pick Japanese! They mastered all the aforementioned subjects.<br/><br/>Well, I&apos;ve got a very mixed feelings about this book. On one hand I enjoyed it, the writing style and the main idea, but I got lost about &quot;why?&quot; and &quot;so?...&quot;. Anyway, <b>3.5 stars</b> is pretty fair, it seems to me.</span>
  <span id="freeText11894297084065078668" style="display:none">If you look for <s>fuckery</s> intrigue, especially tagged with such words as "women", "revenge", "manipulation" and "wtf is going on here" - pick Japanese! They mastered all the aforementioned subjects.<br /><br />Well, I've got a very mixed feelings about this book. On one hand I enjoyed it, the writing style and the main idea, but I got lost about "why?" and "so?...". Anyway, <b>3.5 stars</b> is pretty fair, it seems to me.</span>
