              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer681300621823096002">Bewitching and original plot with gripping characters – though all troubled and troubling in their own right – presented in an outstanding modern translation. Simply a joy to read, while the developments long linger in the mind afterwards. Mishima was right: <i>Masks</i> is an esoteric masterpiece.</span>

